### Thought ###
To find the best-rated Thai restaurant in Urbana, IL that serves duck cuisine, I will use Google Maps to search for Thai restaurants in the area. I will then review the ratings and customer comments to identify the best-rated restaurant that serves duck dishes. After gathering the feedback, I will summarize the positive and negative comments in Google Keep Notes. 

### Plan ###
1. Open Google Maps.
2. Search for "Thai restaurant Urbana IL duck cuisine."
3. Review the search results and identify the best-rated restaurant.
4. Read customer reviews for the selected restaurant, focusing on comments about duck dishes.
5. Open Google Keep Notes and summarize the positive and negative feedback.
6. Save the summary in Keep Notes.

### Current Subgoal ###
Open Google Maps.
